<B>Company Information:</B><BR>
The patented MZX thin speakers deliver exceptionally clear sound. They accurately reproduce an extended range with no cone speaker components and no external power. The light weight and configurational flexibility permit shelf or floor-standing, wall-hung ( with desired framing and artwork ), or in-wall models that can fit beautifully in any décor.<BR>


